            . I lost my shirt out of my garden, where it was hung up to dry, after having been washed; it was safe a few minutes before it was stolen. In consequence of some information which I received, I saw the prisoner at the bar take my shirt out of a handkerchief, and throw it on a hedge: he was laid hold of after running right round the field; there is no path goes near my garden.</p>
